Version 1.0.15¶

  • Unknown HTTP method ‚OPTIONS‘
  • „cercle vicieux“ wegen Fehlalarm „Date range overlaps with ISIP #1“. Wrote new testcase test02.
  • Tx25 kennt jetzt „Pseudo-Nationalnummern“ (PseudoNationalNumbers)
  • watch_tim: Had to completely rewrite swapclass because it wasn’t able to handle conversion situations (1) from Household to Client or (2) from Person to Household
